import React from 'react'

import Chart from '../Chart/Chart';
const dataPoints = [
  {label: 'Jan', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Feb', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Mar', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Apr', Value: 0},
  {label: 'May', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Jun', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Jul', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Aug', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Sep', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Oct', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Nav', Value: 0},
  {label: 'Dec', Value: 0},
]
const ExpensesChart = () => {
  return (
    <Chart expense={dataPoints}/>
  )
}

export default ExpensesChart
